data.description: Nestled in a quaint neighborhood, this delightful bungalow exudes timeless charm and character. With three bedrooms, one bath, a basement, and a loft, this home offers both space and versatility for your lifestyle. The exterior boasts full brick construction. Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the warm and inviting ambiance. Beautiful wood floors offer a touch of elegance and comfort. The centerpiece of the living space is a charming gas fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings and gatherings.The kitchen offers functionality and style, making meal preparation a pleasure. As you approach, you'll be greeted by a spacious lot, providing room for outdoor activities and gardening. Conveniently located to nearby parks and shopping.  Easy access to I-77. New gutter guards, kitchen counter tops and a 3 ton HVAC replaced in 2023 plus an above ground pool!
